<h1 id="installation">Installation</h1>

<p>Tizonia is available in the repository of most Linux distros as well as Ubuntu, Debian, Linux Mint, Arch Linux and others, and it is also possible to install via snap and Docker</p>

<p>If your system is Debian or Ubuntu, just run this command using the curl command:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">curl <span class="nt">-kL</span> https://goo.gl/Vu8qGR | bash</code></pre></figure>

